                     ) as they had formerly born the yoke of Labors, 

                        Iſaacſons Chro. ſo now of Torture; or rather were both together unyoked, with the Reſt of Martyrdom: Saint Peter being crucified! Inverſly (ſaith Euſebius) to differ from his Maſter; and Saint Paul beheaded! by the tyranny of Nero, who hence was juſtly ſtiled, Dedicator condemnationis Chriſtianae. The Founder of thoſe Ten Chriſtian Perſecutions.

